# 🧬 Enzyme Kinetics Visualizer

A professional simulation tool to model drug-enzyme interactions.

## 🚀 [CLICK HERE FOR LIVE DEMO](https://kiruthiganesan2020-blip.github.io/Enzyme-Kinetics-Visualiser/)

## 🛠 Features
- **Real-time Modeling:** Competitive, Non-competitive, and Uncompetitive inhibition.
- **Drug Presets:** Includes Lisinopril, Simvastatin, and Aspirin data.
- **Analytical Charts:** Dynamic Michaelis-Menten and Lineweaver-Burk plots.

